# Implemented features

This index lists features that have completed implementation, documentation reconciliation, validation, and delivery.

Each feature record explains:

- delivered user-visible behavior;
- architecture integration;
- operational impact;
- validation evidence;
- intentional changes from the original design;
- related documentation, Beads root, commits, and pull requests.

Planned or partially implemented features remain in [Planned Features](../planned-features.md) and Beads. They are added here only during close-out.

